  m_text: 'first you will begin your 100 second Prep Round in the kitchen:


    -Use
    arrow keys to move your chef around the kitchen

    -In the kitchen there will
    be highlighted mini-game boxes that you must enter to start a mini-game.

    -Complete
    as many mini-games as possible to earn food monsters.


    After the prep round
    you will enter the Battle Ground!


    There you will place food monsters with
    your mouse  to defend your kitchen against aliens

'
